data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Enjoy the Downtown Palm Harbor Lifestyle in this Maintenance-Free, Spacious Townhome! You will LOVE this BEAUTIFULLY UPDATED home in the Gated Villas of San Marino, offering 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths, Plus an Open Loft Area, and Spacious 2 Car Garage! This Townhome is SPOTLESS and Refreshed with New Floors, New Interior and Exterior Paint, and New Landscaping. Great Room Floor Plan with Neutral Colors and Coastal Wood-Like Luxury Vinyl in all Living Spaces - Shows Light & Bright. Pocket Sliders lead to a Spacious Screened in Porch with Outdoor Kitchen & Extended Pavered Area that makes Indoor/Outdoor living a Breeze. Large Kitchen with Granite Countertops, Breakfast Bar, Coffee Bar with Wine Fridge & Storage, Island and Custom Cabinets with Crown Molding. Upstairs you'll find a Large Master Suite with New Carpet & Large Walk-In Closet with Organizers. En-Suite Master Bath features Granite Countertops, Dual Sinks & Step-In Shower. 2 Generous Sized Bedrooms, both with New Carpet share adjacent Guest Bath with Dual Sinks & Granite Countertops. Open Loft features the same Wood-like Flooring and could be used as a Playroom, Home Office, or Man Cave. The Rooms are all very Spacious and Downstairs is a Half Bath off the Entry for Convenience that is perfect for guests. Large Upstairs Laundry Room is very Functional. HURRICANE IMPACT WINDOWS AND SLIDERS. HOA fee of $478 a month-Includes Community Pool, Roof, Ground Maintenance, Trash Removal, Basic Cable and Internet. Great Location - Walking Distance to Parks, Pinellas Trail, and Waterfront Pier, as well as A-Rated Schools! Close to Shopping, Tons of Restaurants, County Parks, Beautiful Beaches and Tampa International Airport.
